- Show scrum cards in a grid-like layout: 0, 1/2, 1, 2, 3, 5, 8, 13, 20, 40, 100, ?, infinity, coffee
- On single tap a scrum card is shown with an animation
- On another single tap on a shown scrum card it is hidden with an animation
- On slide left navigation to the previous card
- On slide right navigation to the next card
- Use some custom visually appealing font
- Show attribution information, version, some brief info (About menu)
- Make sure that the app works in Chrome as well
- Allow to customize the background and appearance of the cards: few predefined themes?
- Tests and some build infrastructure for the app?